2026-04-28T06:18:12.4420034Z 22    <!--
2026-04-28T06:18:12.4420579Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-04-28T06:18:12.4421254Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-04-28T06:18:12.4421884Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-04-28T06:18:12.4422686Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-04-28T06:18:12.4423527Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-04-28T06:18:12.4424383Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-04-28T06:18:12.4425215Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-04-28T06:18:12.4426208Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-04-28T06:18:12.4426967Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-04-28T06:18:12.4427627Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-04-28T06:18:12.4428190Z 33    -->
