2026-04-28T06:18:12.6970296Z 26            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-04-28T06:18:12.6971076Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-04-28T06:18:12.6971830Z 28            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-04-28T06:18:12.6972591Z 29        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
